        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 0px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 2px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;    
              line-height: 1.5; 
              margin-top:2px;
            ">Did you know the President of the United States receives a top-secret briefing on national security every morning?</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;  
              line-height: 1.5;
            "><strong>In this edition:</strong></p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              padding-left: 10px; 
            ">→ Westerners visit North Korea</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              padding-left: 10px;
            ">→ IBM acquires HashiCorp</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              padding-left: 10px;
            ">→ Duolingo owl returns</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="0px 0px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <!-- breaking news1  -->
    <!-- /breaking news 1 -->
    <mj-spacer height="10px" />
    <!-- Spotlight -->
    <mj-section css-class="mj_fsection" background-color="#ffffff" css-class="mj_fsection">
      <mj-column background-color="#ffffff" width="100%">
        <mj-text padding="2px 12px 0px 12px" font-family="TNYAdobeCaslonPro, 'Times New Roman', serif;" color="white">
          <h2 style="
          padding-top:14px;
          padding-bottom:8px; 
          color:#4D3060;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom:2px solid #4D3060; 
            
              font-size: 26px;
              line-height: 1.2; 
              font-weight: 400;
               
            ">Spotlight</h2>  
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="TNYAdobeCaslonPro, 'Times New Roman', serif;" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="
              font-size: 24px; 
              line-height: 1.2; 
              font-weight: 400;
              margin-top: 2px !important; 
            ">Musk joins the cabinet</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/elon-musk-trump-cabinet-meeting.png" alt="Elon Musk was present at the Cabinet meeting of Trump’s administration" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;">Elon Musk was present at the Cabinet meeting of Trump’s administration. Credits: Getty Images</p>
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">During President Donald Trump’s first Cabinet meeting, it was clear that Elon Musk had <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-28-02-2025-h1-1-taken-a-dominant-role-in-the-administration?source=website" target="_blank">taken a dominant role in the administration</a>. While the Cabinet members mainly remained silent, Musk spoke three times longer than anyone else. Trump praised Musk’s efforts to reform the government. He added that people unhappy with Elon would be thrown out of the cabinet.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;filter:blur(5px);">Musk, sporting his usual black wool coat and MAGA hat, spoke about fixing the government with his "DOGE" team. He added that he has been receiving a lot of flak and death threats since forming the team. Despite some pushback from certain Cabinet members over the mail sent to federal employees, Musk thanked the cabinet for their support.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-spacer height="15px"></mj-spacer>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>